Concept

Simplify Your Finances and Achieve Your Goals

Our comprehensive expense tracking tool offers a range of powerful features designed to make managing your finances easier. From automatic transaction parsing and manual entry to AI-driven insights, these key features ensure you stay organized, on budget, and on track toward your financial aspirations.

Automatic Expense Tracking

Easily track your transactions through SMS notifications. Our system extracts essential details like bank information, amount, and merchant, so you don’t have to.

Manual Expense Entry

Add expenses manually and categorize them as you like. Stay in control of your spending by tracking across various categories, payment methods, and merchants.

Customizable Alerts

Set alerts for specific spending categories. Get notified when you exceed your set limits, helping you to better manage your budget.

Goal Setting & Tracking

Whether it’s a short-term, mid-term, or long-term goal, set up personalized goals with specific amounts and timeframes. Our app will remind you to save regularly to meet your objectives.

Fordo GPT

Create a smart shopping list and let our AI memorize your purchases. It even predicts future expenses, helping you budget smarter!

Expense GPT (Premium)

Need financial advice? Our AI analyzes your spending behavior and provides personalized financial plans. Set goals based on AI suggestions and watch your savings grow.
